00:02:00.035 --> 00:02:03.200
the new caffeine, the two most
popular styles of meditation

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.290
and how they affect
the brain differently,

00:02:05.290 --> 00:02:07.102
when stress is
actually good for you.

00:02:07.102 --> 00:02:09.060
Stress is getting sort
