00:09:21.330 --> 00:09:26.320
which I think is-- oh,
hello, that wasn't me--

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.780
which is actually a great title.

00:09:27.780 --> 00:09:30.510
And it's a
mindfulness-based training.

00:09:30.510 --> 00:09:33.079
I had the great, good fortune
