00:09:33.079 --> 00:09:34.870
when he was just starting
the Search Inside

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:37.790
Yourself training.

00:09:37.790 --> 00:09:40.790
There's mindfulness, which is
basically a directed attentions

00:09:40.790 --> 00:09:42.590
