00:21:18.150 --> 00:21:20.660
imagine that there's four
quadrants in the brain.

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:23.160
In your waking state, these
two quadrants light up.

00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:25.180
And then, when you
meditate, these go dark.

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:26.969
And these two light up.

00:21:26.969 --> 00:21:28.510
So basically, when
you're meditating,

00:21:28.510 --> 00:21:32.260
you have a different brain than
