parts of the brain.

00:21:53.390 --> 00:21:55.680
And after enough times
of going back and forth

00:21:55.680 --> 00:21:57.970
between the states
of consciousness,

00:21:57.970 --> 00:22:01.470
the brain starts firing
on all cylinders.

