00:39:26.480 --> 00:39:28.146
I want to give you
at least five minutes

00:39:28.146 --> 00:39:30.280
to go to your next
1 o'clock meeting.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:32.424
So let's try a
little meditation.

00:39:32.424 --> 00:39:34.590
So we'll start with this
alternate nostril breathing

00:39:34.590 --> 00:39:35.260
technique.

00:39:35.260 --> 00:39:37.176
And then I'll give you
a guided visualization,

00:39:37.176 --> 00:39:40.990
and we'll try just a few
minutes of a silent practice.

00:39:40.990 --> 00:39:42.996
So if you have
phones or computers,

00:39:42.996 --> 00:39:44.620
you want to put those
things on silent.

00:39:44.620 --> 00:39:46.120
That would be swell.

00:39:46.120 --> 00:39:47.630
And we'll all take
our right hand.

00:39:47.630 --> 00:39:49.630
And don't worry-- we'll
all look silly together.

00:39:49.630 --> 00:39:51.070
And just close
your right nostril.

00:39:51.070 --> 00:39:54.070
And exhale through
your left nostril.

00:39:54.070 --> 00:39:57.704
And then inhale
through your left.

00:39:57.704 --> 00:39:58.370
And then switch.

00:39:58.370 --> 00:40:00.140
Close your left nostril
with your ring finger.

00:40:00.140 --> 00:40:01.390
And exhale through your right.

00:40:04.140 --> 00:40:05.139
Good.

00:40:05.139 --> 00:40:06.180
Inhale through the right.

00:40:09.269 --> 00:40:11.060
And then switch, closing
the right nostril,

00:40:11.060 --> 00:40:12.185
exhaling through your left.

00:40:15.664 --> 00:40:16.830
And inhale through the left.

00:40:19.925 --> 00:40:21.800
And then switching,
closing the left nostril,

00:40:21.800 --> 00:40:22.925
exhaling through the right.

00:40:22.925 --> 00:40:25.510
So this will be our pattern--
out, in on one side, and out,

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:26.270
in on the other.

00:40:26.270 --> 00:40:27.936
And you can go ahead
and close your eyes

00:40:27.936 --> 00:40:30.502
and start to do this
in your own time.

00:40:30.502 --> 00:40:32.460
What I'm interested in
is that when you inhale,

00:40:32.460 --> 00:40:36.950
you fill your lungs all the
way to their full capacity,

00:40:36.950 --> 00:40:39.350
and that when you
exhale, you completely

00:40:39.350 --> 00:40:41.600
empty your lungs to the
very bottom of your exhale.

00:40:45.920 --> 00:40:48.770
And you'll start to notice is
that at the top of your inhale,

00:40:48.770 --> 00:40:51.522
there's a little, tiny space
before you begin the exhale.

00:40:51.522 --> 00:40:53.730
And you don't have to force
that or push it, but just

00:40:53.730 --> 00:40:57.200
allow yourself to float
there for even instance.

00:40:57.200 --> 00:40:58.200
And then the same thing.

00:40:58.200 --> 00:40:59.658
At the bottom of
the exhale, you'll

00:40:59.658 --> 00:41:02.140
notice that there's
a tiny little space.

00:41:02.140 --> 00:41:04.640
Allow yourself to notice that,
and float there at the bottom

00:41:04.640 --> 00:41:05.980
before you begin the inhale.

00:41:11.660 --> 00:41:13.850
Let's try this for
a few more cycles.

00:41:13.850 --> 00:41:16.570
But now I want you to
imagine that on the inhale,

00:41:16.570 --> 00:41:18.720
that you're bringing this
breath and this energy up

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:22.260
through the base of your
spine, letting it travel up

00:41:22.260 --> 00:41:24.540
through your spine, and
then exhaling, and sending

00:41:24.540 --> 00:41:26.623
that breath and that energy
out through the middle

00:41:26.623 --> 00:41:28.520
of your forehead.

00:41:28.520 --> 00:41:41.090
This is creating a beautiful
cycle of breath and energy,

00:41:41.090 --> 00:41:43.430
really enjoying
the full expansion

00:41:43.430 --> 00:41:45.075
of your lungs and
the full exhale.

00:41:47.534 --> 00:41:49.700
As you're inhaling, imagining
that breath and energy

00:41:49.700 --> 00:41:52.283
coming up through the base and
traveling up through your spine

00:41:52.283 --> 00:41:55.000
and then sending that energy
and that creative energy out

00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:56.500
through the middle
of your forehead.

00:42:08.320 --> 00:42:11.510
And the next time you come to
an exhale on the left side,

00:42:11.510 --> 00:42:13.740
you can keep your eyes
closed, but gently

00:42:13.740 --> 00:42:16.920
drop your hands into your lap.

00:42:16.920 --> 00:42:20.200
And I'll walk you through
